    {
      "passage_text": "The staff of bank are Mr A, Mr B, Mrs C, Miss D, Mr E and Miss F. The positions they occupy are manager, assistant manager, cashier, stenographer, teller and a clerk, though not necessarily in that order. The assistant manager is manager's grandson, cashier is stenographer's son-in-law. Mr A is bachelor. Miss D is teller's step sister and Mr E is manager's neighbour. Mr B cannot have a grandson or son-in-law as he is only 20 yr old.",
